Amazing! Hands down one of the best restaurants for breakfast in North Phoenix. It is clean, the food is delish and out server, Ms. Divina, is fantastic. She went out of her way to ensure we were satisfied! If you want a great experience, sit in her section. The cost is reasonable too - approx $10 a person. Oh, and if u are a hot tea drinker like me, they have an excellent variety to choose from.  The time is 7:48 am and they are already busy!

