Fresh, delicious food - very authentic!! They fly in famous singers for live music every weekend! For all you hooka lovers they have a menu of different types of tobacco. All smoking is done outside which I love coming home with my hair still smelling beautiful. All of their hummus and baba are made daily. This is one start us restaurant that I hope to see around for a long time. If you come in the evening ask for Steven. He's the bartender and is absolutely fabulous.

